                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020918-52-off275 t18020918-52-cd276"></join>, four pounds weight of cotton, value 5s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18020918-52-victim406" type="victimName">
